metadata.name: Paper Ape #1
metadata.description: So, you've paperhanded your Bored Ape NFT, huh? That's like selling your moonbag after one green candle, bro. It's weak hands AF, and you're missing out on those sweet diamond hands gains. Don't be a rug-puller, hodl tight and ride the bull market wave. Otherwise, you'll be getting #rekt and FUDding like a n00b.
